  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Donate sanitary pads to 500 schoolgirls in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We will buy sanitary pads and give them to 500 poor girls in a school in rural Kampala, in Uganda. The number of girls dropping out of school increase as they have reached puberty. Stigma around menstruation is one of the reasons for this. We give out reusable sanitary pads as well as educate the girls about menstrual health and practices. The objective of this project is to eliminate stigma, educate youth, and keep 50 girls in school.</narrative>
  </description>
